## Four application questions, explicitly answered

1. **Audio experience (yes):** St. Olaf Music BA, DAWs since 5th grade (15+ yrs), wedding DJ, Python MIDI bridge (production, live gigs). Answer in cover letter paragraph 1 and one-pager credential cards.
2. **Technologies:** Python (rtmidi), Web Audio API (AudioContext, OfflineAudioContext, Wilson scheduler), Ableton/Logic/Pro Tools, plus engineering stack (React, Angular, .NET, Python, SQL). Answered explicitly in Q2 block.
3. **Role:** Sole developer and architect on personal audio projects; SME on 60k-line US Bank platform. Answered in Q3 block.
4. **Links:** demo + portfolio, both in cover letter Q4 block and as CTA in every deliverable.

